00:00:00.110 --> 00:00:12.339
Tips on the Baby Scratch (Most basic scratch)
This scratch was given birth by Grand Mater

00:00:12.339 --> 00:00:33.540
Theodore in 1975.

00:00:33.540 --> 00:01:04.079
You must use an open fader. 1. With you left
hand push the record forward and backwards.

00:01:04.079 --> 00:01:16.659
(Don't take finger off the record). Slide
finger back and forth. 2. Put to music and

00:01:16.659 --> 00:01:45.520
began to scratch. Make sure that you are using
the push and pull hand method. 3. When mixing

00:01:45.520 --> 00:02:03.829
up the scratch, you can make your hand move
faster or slower depending on the beat. 4.

00:02:03.829 --> 00:02:07.939
Make sure you know where your record is marked;
so that you know where the scratch starts.

00:02:07.939 --> 00:02:15.980
Have the record marked at the needle point
and off to the side. This way you know where

00:02:15.980 --> 00:02:24.670
to began your scratch.

